## HANNA Tor client profile for OSINT scraping
## Client-only mode: no relay/exit behavior.

## SOCKS endpoint for internal workers.
SocksPort 9050 IsolateDestAddr IsolateSOCKSAuth

## Control channel for circuit rotation (internal network only).
ControlPort 9051
CookieAuthentication 1

## Explicitly disable HTTP tunnel listener for this profile.
HTTPTunnelPort 0

## Hardening and runtime behavior.
DisableDebuggerAttachment 1
UseEntryGuards 1
NumEntryGuards 3
MaxClientCircuitsPending 1000
CircuitBuildTimeout 60
ConnLimit 1000

## Logs are kept in mounted isolated runtime path.
Log notice file /var/log/tor/notices.log
Log warn file /var/log/tor/warns.log
